  "excerpt": "<p>My Etsy Picks: Here Comes Peter Cottontail *Here comes Peter Cottontail, hoppin’ down the bunny trail, hippity hoppin’ Easter’s on its way!* -Anyone else remember this song/movie? Let’s celebrate the upcoming holiday with some really adorable handmade Easter themed items found on Etsy! There were SO many to choose from, but these were my favorites.</p>\n",
  "content": "<p><strong>My Etsy Picks: Here Comes Peter Cottontail</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><em>*Here comes Peter Cottontail, hoppin’ down the bunny trail, hippity hoppin’ Easter’s on its way!* </em>-Anyone else remember this song/movie?</p></blockquote>\n<p>Let’s celebrate the upcoming holiday with some really adorable handmade Easter themed items found on Etsy! There were SO many to choose from, but these were my favorites.</p>\n<p>Pop on over to the <a title=\"Here Comes Peter Cottontail Etsy Treasury by Katie Crafts\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyNDgyNTc1Mw/here-comes-peter-cottontail\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>original treasury right here</strong></a> and give it a heart if you love it too! When you’re all done checking out the amazing shops below, feel free to stay and watch <em>“Here Comes Peter Cottontail,”</em> the 1971 Easter TV special that I loved as a kid (but that looking back is a little creepy). The full movie is below! Enjoy!</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Bondurant Mountain Art on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/123465488/needle-felted-easter-bunny-with-1-carrot?ref=tre-2724825753-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bondurant Mountain Art</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Tricky Pony Arts on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/183108573/easter-eggs-set-of-2-ceramic-hand?ref=tre-2724825753-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tricky Pony Arts</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Sew June Jones on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/223089968/felt-chick-pdf-pattern-easter-chick?ref=tre-2724825753-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sew June Jones</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Hillbilly and Me on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/223560859/easter-peeps-easter-decor-spring-decor?ref=tre-2724825753-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hillbilly and Me</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Banner Cheer Jr. on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/200621815/happy-easter-decoration-happy-easter?ref=tre-2724825753-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Banner Cheer JR</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Corner House Shoppe on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/183888351/set-of-10-happy-little-felted-wool?ref=tre-2724825753-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Corner House Shoppe</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"MINIMETRY on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/126628023/fabric-carrot-easter-decor?ref=tre-2724825753-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">MINIMETRY</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"HC Woodcraft on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/123576031/personalized-wooden-easter-egg-natural?ref=tre-2724825753-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">HC Woodcraft</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"AJ Sweet Soap on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/220939609/marshmallow-easter-bunny-soap-set-spring?ref=tre-2724825753-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">AJ Sweet Soap</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"1000 Painted Trees on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/183430475/easter-bunny-painting-decoration-for?ref=tre-2724825753-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1000 Painted Trees</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Less Candles on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/185162766/easter-candle-egg-handmade-gold-painted?ref=tre-2724825753-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Less Candles</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Ever Blooming Original on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/125934647/mini-easter-wreath-bunny-wreath-spring?ref=tre-2724825753-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ever Blooming Original</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Bubbly Tea Shop on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/207260578/easter-bunny-plush-easter-decor-easter?ref=tre-2724825753-13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bubbly Tea Shop</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Creative Applique on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/178465752/1st-easter-bunny-machine-embroidery?ref=tre-2724825753-14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Creative Applique</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Mama Do That on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/222901967/easter-basket-filler-baby-lamb-waldorf?ref=tre-2724825753-15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mama Do That</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Nail Thins on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/125862117/bunny-nail-decals-easter-bunnies-by?ref=tre-2724825753-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Nail Thins</a></strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">Which Easter item was your favorite? Did you watch “Here Comes Peter Cottontail”?</p>\n",
